{"data":[{"name":"77:1","price":"Par ceux qu’on envoie en rafales [1016].","arabic":"وَٱلۡمُرۡسَلَٰتِ عُرۡفٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5623,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"[1016] Ceux qu’on envoie…: Littér.: les envoyées les unes derrière les autres. D’après le contexte et la tradition, il s’agit des vents (qui sont féminins, en arabe), et spécialement des vents de destruction.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:2","price":"et qui soufflent en tempête !","arabic":"فَٱلۡعَٰصِفَٰتِ عَصۡفٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5624,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:3","price":"Et qui dispersent largement [dans toutes les directions].","arabic":"وَٱلنَّٰشِرَٰتِ نَشۡرٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5625,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:4","price":"Par ceux qui séparent nettement (le bien et le mal) [1017],","arabic":"فَٱلۡفَٰرِقَٰتِ فَرۡقٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5626,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"[1017] Ceux qui séparent: Les Anges qui portent les ordres d’Allah aux messagers.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:5","price":"et lancent un rappel.","arabic":"فَٱلۡمُلۡقِيَٰتِ ذِكۡرًا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5627,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:6","price":"En guise d’excuse ou d’avertissement[1018] !","arabic":"عُذۡرًا أَوۡ نُذۡرًا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5628,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"[1018] En guise d’excuse: après la venue du message les hommes n’auront plus d’excuse.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:7","price":"Ce qui vous est promis est inéluctable.","arabic":"إِنَّمَا تُوعَدُونَ لَوَٰقِعٞ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5629,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:8","price":"Quand donc les étoiles seront effacées,","arabic":"فَإِذَا ٱلنُّجُومُ طُمِسَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5630,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:9","price":"et que le ciel sera fendu,","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلسَّمَآءُ فُرِجَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5631,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:10","price":"et que les montagnes seront pulvérisées,","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡجِبَالُ نُسِفَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5632,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:11","price":"et que le moment (pour la réunion) des Messagers a été fixé! ...","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلرُّسُلُ أُقِّتَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5633,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:12","price":"A quel jour tout cela a-t-il été renvoyé?","arabic":"لِأَيِّ يَوۡمٍ أُجِّلَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5634,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:13","price":"Au Jour de la Décision. [le Jugement]!","arabic":"لِيَوۡمِ ٱلۡفَصۡلِ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5635,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:14","price":"Et qui te dira ce qu’est le Jour de la Décision ?","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا يَوۡمُ ٱلۡفَصۡلِ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5636,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:15","price":"Malheur, ce jour-là, à ceux qui criaient au mensonge.","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5637,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:16","price":"N’avons-Nous pas fait périr les premières [générations] ?","arabic":"أَلَمۡ نُهۡلِكِ ٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5638,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:17","price":"Puis ne les avons-Nous pas fait suivre par les derniers ?","arabic":"ثُمَّ نُتۡبِعُهُمُ ٱلۡأٓخِرِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5639,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:18","price":"C’est ainsi que Nous agissons avec les criminels.","arabic":"كَذَٰلِكَ نَفۡعَلُ بِٱلۡمُجۡرِمِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5640,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:19","price":"Malheur, ce jour-là, à ceux qui criaient au mensonge.","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5641,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:20","price":"Ne vous avons-Nous pas créés d’une eau vile [1019].","arabic":"أَلَمۡ نَخۡلُقكُّم مِّن مَّآءٖ مَّهِينٖ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5642,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"[1019] Une eau vile: le liquide spermatique.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:21","price":"que Nous avons placée dans un reposoir sûr [1020],","arabic":"فَجَعَلۡنَٰهُ فِي قَرَارٖ مَّكِينٍ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5643,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"[1020] Reposoir sûr: le ventre de la mère.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:22","price":"pour une durée connue ?","arabic":"إِلَىٰ قَدَرٖ مَّعۡلُومٖ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5644,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:23","price":"Nous l’avons décrété ainsi et Nous décrétons [tout] de façon parfaite.","arabic":"فَقَدَرۡنَا فَنِعۡمَ ٱلۡقَٰدِرُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5645,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:24","price":"Malheur, ce jour-là, à ceux qui criaient au mensonge.","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5646,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:25","price":"N’avons-Nous pas fait de la terre un endroit les contenant tous,","arabic":"أَلَمۡ نَجۡعَلِ ٱلۡأَرۡضَ كِفَاتًا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5647,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:26","price":"les vivants ainsi que les morts ?","arabic":"أَحۡيَآءٗ وَأَمۡوَٰتٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5648,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:27","price":"Et n’y avons-Nous pas placé fermement de hautes montagnes ? Et ne vous avons-Nous pas abreuvés d’eau douce ?","arabic":"وَجَعَلۡنَا فِيهَا رَوَٰسِيَ شَٰمِخَٰتٖ وَأَسۡقَيۡنَٰكُم مَّآءٗ فُرَاتٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5649,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:28","price":"Malheur, ce jour-là, à ceux qui criaient au mensonge.","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5650,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:29","price":"Allez vers ce que vous traitiez alors de mensonge !","arabic":"ٱنطَلِقُوٓاْ إِلَىٰ مَا كُنتُم بِهِۦ تُكَذِّبُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5651,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:30","price":"Allez vers une ombre [fumée de l’Enfer] à trois branches ;","arabic":"ٱنطَلِقُوٓاْ إِلَىٰ ظِلّٖ ذِي ثَلَٰثِ شُعَبٖ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5652,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:31","price":"qui n’est ni ombreuse ni capable de protéger contre la flamme ;","arabic":"لَّا ظَلِيلٖ وَلَا يُغۡنِي مِنَ ٱللَّهَبِ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5653,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:32","price":"car [le feu] jette des étincelles volumineuses comme des châteaux,","arabic":"إِنَّهَا تَرۡمِي بِشَرَرٖ كَٱلۡقَصۡرِ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5654,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:33","price":"et qu’on prendrait pour des chameaux jaunes.","arabic":"كَأَنَّهُۥ جِمَٰلَتٞ صُفۡرٞ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5655,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:34","price":"Malheur, ce jour-là, à ceux qui criaient au mensonge.","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5656,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:35","price":"Ce sera le jour où ils ne [peuvent] pas parler,","arabic":"هَٰذَا يَوۡمُ لَا يَنطِقُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5657,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:36","price":"et point ne leur sera donné permission de s’excuser.","arabic":"وَلَا يُؤۡذَنُ لَهُمۡ فَيَعۡتَذِرُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5658,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:37","price":"Malheur, ce jour-là, à ceux qui criaient au mensonge.","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5659,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:38","price":"C’est le Jour de la Décision [Jugement], où nous vous réunirons ainsi que les anciens.","arabic":"هَٰذَا يَوۡمُ ٱلۡفَصۡلِۖ جَمَعۡنَٰكُمۡ وَٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5660,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:39","price":"Si vous disposez d’une ruse, rusez donc contre Moi.","arabic":"فَإِن كَانَ لَكُمۡ كَيۡدٞ فَكِيدُونِ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5661,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:40","price":"Malheur, ce jour-là, à ceux qui criaient au mensonge.","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5662,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:41","price":"Les pieux seront parmi des ombrages et des sources.","arabic":"إِنَّ ٱلۡمُتَّقِينَ فِي ظِلَٰلٖ وَعُيُونٖ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5663,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:42","price":"De même que des fruits selon leurs désirs.","arabic":"وَفَوَٰكِهَ مِمَّا يَشۡتَهُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5664,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:43","price":"“Mangez et buvez agréablement, pour ce que vous faisiez.”","arabic":"كُلُواْ وَٱشۡرَبُواْ هَنِيٓـَٔۢا بِمَا كُنتُمۡ تَعۡمَلُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5665,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:44","price":"C’est ainsi que Nous récompensons les bienfaisants.","arabic":"إِنَّا كَذَٰلِكَ نَجۡزِي ٱلۡمُحۡسِنِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5666,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:45","price":"Malheur, ce jour-là, à ceux qui criaient au mensonge.","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5667,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:46","price":"“Mangez et jouissez un peu (ici-bas); vous êtes certes des criminels”.","arabic":"كُلُواْ وَتَمَتَّعُواْ قَلِيلًا إِنَّكُم مُّجۡرِمُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5668,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:47","price":"Malheur, ce jour-là, à ceux qui criaient au mensonge.","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5669,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:48","price":"Et quand on leur dit : “Inclinez-vous [1021], ils ne s’inclinent pas.","arabic":"وَإِذَا قِيلَ لَهُمُ ٱرۡكَعُواْ لَا يَرۡكَعُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5670,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"[1021] Inclinez-vous: «Faites la Ṣalāt».","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:49","price":"Malheur, ce jour-là, à ceux qui criaient au mensonge.","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5671,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"77:50","price":"Après cela, en quelle parole croiront-ils donc [1022] ?","arabic":"فَبِأَيِّ حَدِيثِۭ بَعۡدَهُۥ يُؤۡمِنُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5672,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"[1022] A la fin de cette Sourate, il est bon de dire: «Nous croyons en Allah».","lang":"fr"}],"chapter":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat","Chapter Al-Mursalat","Mursalat","Surah Mursalat","Chapter Mursalat","Al Mursalat","Surah Al Mursalat","Chapter Al Mursalat","Surah 77","Chapter 77","The Emissaries","المرسلات"]}